\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
\u8211?En absoluto -dijo-. S\u233? qu\u233? hora es.\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
\u8211?\u191?Ah, s\u237?? \u191?Y qu\u233? hora es?\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{	
